metadata.name: Ledger #1/55
metadata.description: Ledger, created by x0r, is a fully on-chain dynamic NFT that leverages smart contract composability. The ASCII image portrays a subtle x0r logo where the vertical line contains the addresses of all current owners of the NFT. Whenever this NFT transfers, the ASCII art will update and always reflect both the current owners and the last block number where an update occurred.
